This topic  came up in every repository session at #AGU20 so far - why & how to cite data? Why? Helps researchers get credit for their work! How? Add a formal #citation in your paper, mention the #data in a data availability statement, and always use the #DOI. #datahelpdesk https://t.co/Vd5h7R1FWv

Our online catalog helps data be #discoverable, data are licensed as CC-0 or CC-BY at the time of upload to make them #accessible, we encourage semantic annotations to make the data #interoperable, & we have rigorous metadata completeness checks to ensure data are #reusable. 2/2
